tspan.tspan: I'm sure you've been pulled from your lean before
in bloodless warfare by the unreclined.
They flood you, leaner, mired in torture,
bending your frame to fit picture refined
to please their perspective, favouring lines
frantic and sharply angled to viewer -
slicing resting subject with tax and fines
on taking time to admire leisure.
Entitiled owners see terrorism
viewing undemanding hedonism.
"I see wisdom in thumb-sucking baby
but weep too, from knowing a quietude
is found so young by self-sufficiency,
unguarded from insular attitude
and worse the ones that paint themselves abloom -
representation that's not a flower,
flaunting petals still, giving no perfume.
We trusted their promise of an offer
but learned to live life aloof on treason.
I offer my thumb for its our season.
"You take in all labels like scattered seeds,
not one to bite off pacifying thumb -
even those off-green. Parasitic weeds
numb their brain stem for undeserved aplomb.
They tend you so only they propagate
feeding suicide candy to unchecked
demeanours - should they spore, greener worlds wait,
heeding multiplied hands meeting reject,
growing fungi-algae to great effect,
I've only found help from class imperfect."
The leaner laid cradled, captured by thought.
He felt eons pass, felt vestigial,
before now, before he found that unsought
external hand reach out - so trivial,
but then, why so individual too?
He'd lived like others, roots entrenched in ground,
limbs stretched for solitude, alone they grew,
breathing CO2 as clouds danced around.
Rivers dried, animals died, unnoticed.
Now stray branch bridged untapped brain unfocused.
Guided around transistors on motors,
Leaner leads Ironics on the fast track
through the distribution centre's sorters
(few jobs left other than walks there and back).
"I'm told I must guard to get what I need,
When what I need's guarded by me from me.
Why not hire one without need? Indeed,
the fulfilled don't guard what they get for free.
Pharaoh's can't balance needing the needful
And such scant semblance of resource absence."
Leaner cites "waste long-lived radiation
decaying in storage indefinite"
- ram-man registers traces signalling,
spaceman follows him, forking from the rest.
"Data collator," leaner also cites,
"info caught in inescapable pull,
stringified, to leash us to D.T.V."
- rabbit and deer split with the wires.
"All for this centralised trickling out."
Dog and peacock remain to keep the path.
Access was blocked to access control room.
Posed as statue's shadow (Collapse in bronze),
Leaner pre-empts assumed accusation,
"Most would think the sole employed would know this:
cloaked figures guarding what was mine to guard.
This was not my plan, it's not what you're owed -
I'd hope it's clear I don't do my job".
"Nothing is owed," conciliates the snake,
"We are not the kind to recognise debt.
Your purpose is ours, even to submit."
For a hedonist, a call to give up
is consequently a call to action.
Like ox unfound, leaner charged to distract,
cloaked flit around, chasing, hallway's end bound.
Caught in conditioned wind, cloak, abandoned
was fast donned by Owl as Octo and Snake
passed clear entrance to further groups goals.
Ram follows signals through new storage breach.
Rabbit brute forces weakened routing rules.
Dog preps noise on Determinists approach...
